column5: has anybody have any news how the moira river is now?water levels there have been crazy this year.has it subsided yet?hope everybody is ok now in that area. i've been fishing that river system for years and i remember last summer water levels were at its lowest. any fishing report would be nice. thanks
lolol i just made a post you may be interested in. Water levels are still high, but dropping. Most peoples sandbags are at the side of the road now.  -R-
glad to hear water levels are going down now.
